{"tid":2181123,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"今晚 2100 開始 警謊指鹿為馬改寫7.21歷史 《頭條動新聞》Ep.5 和你繼續諷刺時弊 (蘋果日報","createTime":"2020-08-30T11:14:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T14:27:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8bcfbbd746f27be8861e0a71be98c80d1eb2d147","tid":2181123,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T11:14:12.000Z","msg":"#Appledaily #StayHome #WithMe<br />\n<br />\n今晚 2100 開始<br />\n警謊指鹿為馬改寫7.21歷史 《頭條動新聞》Ep.5<br />\n和你繼續諷刺時弊 (蘋果日報 Apple daily)<br />\nAug 30, 2020<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LBOTFToc9so\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLBOTFToc9so&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoJtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=7d439a98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LBOTFToc9so</a><br />\n<br />\n蘋果動新聞 HK Apple Daily<br />\n1.71M subscribers<br />\n<br />\n《AppleDaily Show豪》<br />\n外界狠批7.21警謊指鹿為馬，事後警務署長鄧炳強「補鑊」稱不理想，原來有圖有片亦未必有真相，「Show豪」進入警察的內心世界，面對一幕幕矚目驚心的畫面，為警隊和同袍（白衣人）解畫。<br />\n<br />\n《四點鐘王Sir》<br />\n一名香港警察於八月廿五日傍晚六時繁忙時段，打扮成女人於太子站A出口扶手電梯，偷拍一名女子，後知是駐守投訴警察課的女高級督察裙下春光。這名香港警察的心理缺陷，處心積慮去侵犯對象，這種喬裝行為，已經超越為隱藏犯罪痕迹而做，如披上羊皮的豺狼走入羊群食羊，並不是為增加成功機會，而是要製造羊食羊的可怕事實，令羊群膽破心驚，從中汲取喜悅。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報 ： <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoJtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=09ae0e96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com&h=bbd68420\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com</a><br />\n即 like 蘋果 fb  ： <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoJtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=42a0991e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia</a><br />\niPhone App ： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/AppleDailyApp-iPhone\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FAppleDailyApp-iPhone&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoJtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=913d9e5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/AppleDailyApp-iPhone</a><br />\nAndroid App ： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/AppleDailyApp-Android\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FAppleDailyApp-Android&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoJtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=6f4e9793\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/AppleDailyApp-Android</a>"},{"pid":"931d2895f6d368d4b92a1376a9c5f859a8bd86a6","tid":2181123,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T12:22:58.000Z","msg":"37 mins"},{"pid":"38dd51b1d609bcc4181739734214c771bbec3f58","tid":2181123,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T13:03:16.000Z","msg":"開波"},{"pid":"5df163e14c9ab7bbbedb41c90490835d096de83d","tid":2181123,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T13:03:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef36d354ee1bdfe13e10e00eb638469040148f31","tid":2181123,"uid":58863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T13:05:43.000Z","msg":"brian cha <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5fb83f757c9bc62c0cc12dc585e657d3aab4694","tid":2181123,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T13:26:24.000Z","msg":"四點鐘王SIR"},{"pid":"209fb690e9f2847a5a92e132b07787e44f401344","tid":2181123,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T13:31:22.000Z","msg":"奔跑吧"},{"pid":"469b35d9a25fa7396d3da4a6b16517baae83fbda","tid":2181123,"uid":274996,"like":0,"d